                            <h4>Weekly Souks of Taza: An Immersion into Moroccan Culture and Treasures.</h4>
                        </div>
                        <p>Taza, , is a city renowned for its lively and colorful weekly souks. The weekly souks, also known as "weekly markets" or "livestock markets," are significant events in the social and economic life of the region.</p>
                        <div class="destination-details-image">
                            <a href="destination.html"><img src="/images/sok4.jpg" alt="image"></a>
